ASINTRODUCED
ANACT authorizing the department of education to establish a safe and resilient schools
advisorycouncil.
FISCALIMPACT:
This bill establishes a Safe and Resilient Schools Advisory Council within the Department of
Education and creates a nonlapsing New Hampshire Safe and Resilient Schools Fund to support
theCouncil'sefforts,whichmayreceivestate, federal,orprivatefunding.Anyfund expenditures
shall require approval by the Commissioner of Education, in consultation with the Council, and
approval by the Joint Legislative Fiscal Committee. The Department has identified no costs
relative to this bill and to the extent no appropriation is given to the new fund, this bill is not
expectedtohaveanyfiscalimpact.
